theorem isClosed_closure_diff_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    IsClosed (closure A \ interior A) := by
  simpa [frontier] using frontier_isClosed (X := X) (A := A)

theorem Set.compl_compl {α : Type*} {s : Set α} :
    ((sᶜ)ᶜ : Set α) = s := by
  ext x
  by_cases hx : x ∈ s <;> simp [hx]

theorem interior_closure_frontier_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure (frontier A)) = interior (frontier A) := by
  have h : closure (frontier A) = frontier A :=
    closure_frontier_eq_frontier (X := X) (A := A)
  simpa [h]
